{"tid":1406051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要爭取18區食催淚彈","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:45:04.000Z","uid":59971,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84e2e0e8d3d1fc6c6217775532b8a2d41260f8af","tid":1406051,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到西環個直播<br />\n黑警又射催淚彈上民區老人院 唔比街坊番屋企<br />\n每次出動都不停做柒事 <br />\n<br />\n只要每區都遊行一次 甚至一日分幾區<br />\n黑警落場我地等佢射完彈就轉場 <br />\n好快就會得罪哂所有街坊 支持警犬嘅人  深藍 廢老<br />\n全港阿伯 阿姐 深藍 淺藍 中立 中產 咩職業 都食過催淚彈<br />\n到時全香港人反警犬不是夢<br />\n玩到11月區選<br />\n民建聯成功爭取18區市民食過期催淚彈計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時好似係8/18"},{"pid":"e53fb46a0b1793a5ebed3a5f64cabd60e18a2966","tid":1406051,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7062eeb5759135f88993fa69589c582d7ad9af0d","tid":1406051,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"試下天水圍,黃絲請藍絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba63d22eddd8f2272b63fec42bd36386f67f216","tid":1406051,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7062eeb5759135f88993fa69589c582d7ad9af0d","tid":1406051,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"試下天水圍,黃絲請藍絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"等警犬出手請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adbb21cdb905a4b532bed0dc9dd12e161f45175","tid":1406051,"uid":59971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"365c3804e2e0e3d5d1797e920429879fcc14bb03","tid":1406051,"uid":264083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"廢老：要不是黃尸搞事，警察哥哥點會放催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl